edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.interpreter

Class ExecuteException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.interpreter.InterpreterException
          • edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.interpreter.ExecuteException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ExecuteException
extends InterpreterException
    ExecuteException contains errors or warnings from processing source statements in the interpreter or in the extension libraries. If the application needs to pass through other types of exceptions, it must wrap those exceptions in the constructor.
